Package io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasModule

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseAtlasModule, ConstantModule, CsvModule, DfdlModule, JavaModule, JsonModule, KafkaConnectModule, PropertyModule, XmlModule
public interface AtlasModule
A SPI contract between AtlasMap core and modules. AtlasMap core engine invokes those methods while processing mappings. AtlasModule corresponds to each DataSource/Document one-by-one. It is created from the metadata read from DataSource definition at runtime so that data format specific handling could be performed.
